  <entry>
    <title>question1</title>
    <url>/2022/11/18/question1/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="maximum-number-of-balloons">Maximum Number of Balloons</h3>
<p>Given a string <code>text</code>, you want to use the characters of
<code>text</code> to form as many instances of the word
<strong>"balloon"</strong> as possible.</p>
<p>You can use each character in <code>text</code> <strong>at most
once</strong>. Return the maximum number of instances that can be
formed; <code>1 &lt;= text.length &lt;= 104</code>; <code>text</code>
consists of lower case English letters only</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Example1:</span><br><span class="line">Input: text = <span class="string">&quot;leetcode&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">Output: <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">Example2:</span><br><span class="line">Input: text = <span class="string">&quot;nlaebolko&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">Output: <span class="number">1</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Solution:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 本题实际上是要求返回text中组成&#x27;balloon&#x27;的最小元素个数,所以我们不在乎其他元素的出现个数,只需统计b,a,l,o,n每个元素出现的次数;并且,其中的最小值就是能组成&#x27;ballon&#x27;的最大个数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">maxNumberOfBalloons</span>(<span class="params">text</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">min</span>(text.count(<span class="string">&#x27;b&#x27;</span>), text.count(<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>), text.count(<span class="string">&#x27;l&#x27;</span>)//<span class="number">2</span>, text.count(<span class="string">&#x27;o&#x27;</span>)//<span class="number">2</span>, text.count(<span class="string">&#x27;n&#x27;</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>Python Tests</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Leetcode</tag>
      </tags>
