  <entry>
    <title>question5</title>
    <url>/2022/11/22/question5/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="apply-operations-to-an-array">Apply Operations to an Array</h3>
<p>You are given a <strong>0-indexed</strong> array <code>nums</code> of
size <code>n</code> consisting of <strong>non-negative</strong>
integers.</p>
<p>You need to apply <code>n - 1</code> operations to this array where,
in the <code>ith</code> operation (<strong>0-indexed</strong>), you will
apply the following on the <code>ith</code> element of
<code>nums</code>:</p>
<ul>
<li>If <code>nums[i] == nums[i + 1]</code>, then multiply
<code>nums[i]</code> by <code>2</code> and set <code>nums[i + 1]</code>
to <code>0</code>. Otherwise, you skip this operation.</li>
</ul>
<p>After performing <strong>all</strong> the operations,
<strong>shift</strong> all the <code>0</code>'s to the
<strong>end</strong> of the array.</p>
<ul>
<li>For example, the array <code>[1,0,2,0,0,1]</code> after shifting all
its <code>0</code>'s to the end, is <code>[1,2,1,0,0,0]</code>.</li>
</ul>
<p>Return <em>the resulting array</em>.</p>
<p><strong>Note</strong> that the operations are applied
<strong>sequentially</strong>, not all at once.</p>
<p><strong>Constraints:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><code>2 &lt;= nums.length &lt;= 2000</code></li>
<li><code>0 &lt;= nums[i] &lt;= 1000</code></li>
</ul>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Example:</span></span><br><span class="line">Input: nums = [<span class="number">0</span>,<span class="number">1</span>]</span><br><span class="line">Output: [<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">0</span>]</span><br><span class="line">Explanation: No operation can be applied, we just shift the <span class="number">0</span> to the end.</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Solution:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 只需要做两步: 1.按规则重新赋值;2.列表排序,0移到最后面去</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">applyOperations</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 列表中的第一个数无需处理,所以从1索引开始遍历    </span></span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="built_in">len</span>(n)):</span><br><span class="line">    	<span class="keyword">if</span> n[i] == n[i-<span class="number">1</span>]:</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># python两个变量互换可以直接写,不需要借助temp</span></span><br><span class="line">            n[i-<span class="number">1</span>], n[i] = n[i-<span class="number">1</span>]*<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">0</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># not转为bool值    </span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">sorted</span>(n, key=<span class="keyword">lambda</span> x: <span class="keyword">not</span> x)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在python中, bool值False=0, True=1;</p>
<p><code>[]</code>,<code>&#123;&#125;</code>,<code>''</code>,<code>None</code>,<code>()</code>
,<code>0</code>当这些数据结构为空时, bool(arg)==False,
在上面的解法就是运用了这一点, 判断列表中元素是否为0,
这样就把0全部移到最后面去啦; 如果不适用这个点,同样可以再次遍历列表,
进行判断, 再进行列表的增删操作</p>
]]></content>
