  <entry>
    <title>二叉树遍历</title>
    <url>/2022/11/21/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h3 id="二叉树理解">二叉树理解</h3>
<p><strong>树(Tree):</strong></p>
<p>是存在n(n&gt;=0)个节点的集合结构, 从视觉上看, 像是一棵圣诞树.</p>
<p>组成这棵圣诞树的每个元素称为节点(Node);</p>
<p>每一个树形结构中最顶端的节点称为根节点(Root),
根节点直接连接的节点为其的子节点;</p>
<p>从根节点到最尾端的子节点,每一层都是这颗树的层级(Level);</p>
<p>最大层级就是树的深度(Depth);</p>
<p>总体的树结构可以看成是很多子树(Subtree)的组合.</p>
<img src="/2022/11/21/%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%A0%91%E9%81%8D%E5%8E%86/%E6%A0%91%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-9042239.png" class="">
<p>如图所示, 总体来看的话,这棵树深度为4,
根节点为A;而对于节点D,G,H,I所构成的子树而言,根节点为D,深度为2.</p>
<p><strong>二叉树(Binary Tree):</strong></p>
<p>树形结构的一种,
二叉树限定了每一个根节点下的子节点最多有2个,并且有严格的左右区分</p>
<h3 id="二叉树用处">二叉树用处</h3>
<p>最初我是从排序算法中了解到这个结构, 检索或是插入数据时,
我们可以按一定的规则,比如根节点值&lt;左节点值&lt;右节点值构建一个二叉树结构,
对于指定的数据, 可以很快定位到他所处的位置; 机器学习中的决策树(decision
tree)模型同样也是使用了二叉树结构</p>
<h3 id="二叉树遍历">二叉树遍历</h3>
<p><strong>前序遍历:</strong></p>
<p>根节点--&gt;左节点--&gt;右节点:
从视觉上来感知整个路径,就是从根节点出发,按逆时针方向遍历,每一个子树结构也同样遵循此规则</p>
<p><strong>后序遍历:</strong></p>
<p>左节点--&gt;右节点--&gt;根节点:
方向由树的底部通往顶部,优先左节点,再右节点,最后是根节点;
每一个子树结构按此规则遍历完成后, 再到同层级的子树结构</p>
<p><strong>中序遍历:</strong></p>
<p>左节点--&gt;根节点--&gt;右节点:
这个很好理解,想象将树的每一个节点都垂直投影到平面上,从左到右遍历</p>
<p><strong>层次遍历:</strong></p>
<p>与中序遍历类似, 按层级由左到右进行遍历</p>
<p>推荐阅读<a
href="https://blog.csdn.net/chinesekobe/article/details/110874773">这篇文章</a>,
作者用动画的方式很好的表现了遍历顺序:</p>
<h3 id="二叉树代码构造">二叉树代码构造</h3>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">TreeNode</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">object</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    创建二叉树链表结构</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self, val=<span class="literal">None</span>, left=<span class="literal">None</span>, right=<span class="literal">None</span></span>):</span><br><span class="line">        self.val = val  <span class="comment"># 数据</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.left = left  <span class="comment"># 左节点</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.right = right  <span class="comment"># 右节点</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title class_">BinaryTree</span>(<span class="title class_ inherited__">object</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    二叉树</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        初始化二叉树</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.root = <span class="literal">None</span>  <span class="comment"># 根结点</span></span><br><span class="line">        self.result = <span class="built_in">list</span>()  <span class="comment"># 用于遍历</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">is_empty</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        判断二叉树是否为空</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> self.root <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">None</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">ergodic</span>(<span class="params">self</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        遍历二叉树</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> self.is_empty():</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">&quot;二叉树为空&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="comment"># 递归法</span></span><br><span class="line">            self.preorder_ergodic_recursion(self.root)  <span class="comment"># 前序遍历</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(self.result)</span><br><span class="line">            self.result = <span class="built_in">list</span>()</span><br><span class="line">            self.middle__ergodic_recursion(self.root)  <span class="comment"># 中序遍历</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(self.result)</span><br><span class="line">            self.result = <span class="built_in">list</span>()</span><br><span class="line">            self.afterword__ergodic_recursion(self.root)  <span class="comment"># 后序遍历</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(self.result)</span><br><span class="line">            self.result = <span class="built_in">list</span>()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">preorder_ergodic_recursion</span>(<span class="params">self, data</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        前序遍历：递归法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> data <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> self.result</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            self.result.append(data.val)</span><br><span class="line">            self.preorder_ergodic_recursion(data.left)</span><br><span class="line">            self.preorder_ergodic_recursion(data.right)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">middle__ergodic_recursion</span>(<span class="params">self, data</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        中序遍历：递归法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> data <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> self.result</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            self.middle__ergodic_recursion(data.left)</span><br><span class="line">            self.result.append(data.val)</span><br><span class="line">            self.middle__ergodic_recursion(data.right)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">afterword__ergodic_recursion</span>(<span class="params">self, data</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        后序遍历：递归法</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">        &quot;&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> data <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">return</span> self.result</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            self.afterword__ergodic_recursion(data.left)</span><br><span class="line">            self.afterword__ergodic_recursion(data.right)</span><br><span class="line">            self.result.append(data.val)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> __name__ == <span class="string">&#x27;__main__&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 创建四层二叉树结点</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 命名：层次_结点顺序（空的也占位）</span></span><br><span class="line">    tree = BinaryTree()</span><br><span class="line">    t1_1 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t2_1 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;2&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t2_2 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;3&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t3_1 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;4&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t3_2 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;5&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t3_3 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;6&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t3_4 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;7&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t4_1 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;8&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    t4_2 = TreeNode(<span class="string">&quot;9&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 关联节点</span></span><br><span class="line">    tree.root = t1_1</span><br><span class="line">    t1_1.left = t2_1</span><br><span class="line">    t1_1.right = t2_2</span><br><span class="line">    t2_1.left = t3_1</span><br><span class="line">    t2_1.right = t3_2</span><br><span class="line">    t2_2.left = t3_3</span><br><span class="line">    t2_2.right = t3_4</span><br><span class="line">    t3_1.left = t4_1</span><br><span class="line">    t3_1.right = t4_2</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 打印二叉树是否空</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(tree.is_empty())</span><br><span class="line">    tree.ergodic()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
